  <brief_title>A Phase 1 Study of SP-02L in Relapsed or Refractory Patients With Peripheral T-cell Lymphoma (PTCL) in Korea</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1 Study of SP-02L (Darinaparsin for Injection) in Relapsed or Refractory Patients With Peripheral T-cell Lymphoma (PTCL) in Korea</official_title>
