  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and tolerability of SP-02L monotherapy in
      Korean patients with relapsed or refractory Peripheral T-cell Lymphoma (PTCL).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
